Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separated from the rest of the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy made it to Marineford to rescue \Nhis brother, Ace who was to be executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Ace protected Luffy from Akainu's \Nattack  and lost his life in the process!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, Blackbeard turned up \Nand brought further turmoil!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That pose is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.36,0:04:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Insatiable Akainu! \NLava Fists Pummel Luffy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The HQ building is gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave your post!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody please tell me I'm dreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over the centuries we've kept \Nwatch  over the seas from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe the fort of \Njustice the Navy's citadel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is crumbling before my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blackbeard is the one who caught \NAce and triggered the war
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and now he has Whitebeard's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, all you people of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold me and my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gonna happen to this world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:06:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel the power \Ncoursing through my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What power! It feels like I could control \Neverything in the world at my whim!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you waiting for? \NDoesn't anyone wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm willing to fight you to your \Nhearts' content now! What a shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's start with...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...sinking Marineford into water!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shock Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A building can easily be rebuilt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the island of Marineford is located \Nvirtually in the center of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleet Admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To protect the people of the world who \Nare threatened by rampaging villains,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it is important to them that we are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice that comes from \Nhumanity will never perish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't claim to be able to \Nsink this place so lightly,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you little punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such noble beliefs! Huh? Fleet Admiral-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,defend this place--if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and bring the ship to the \Nisland! We can't leave anyone behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for us! We're coming now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta get out of here alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy's victory must be unquestionable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta survive and leave \Nhere as Pops told us to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the pirates know the power \Nof justice through fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Justice...\N--...Through fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Now is the chance to \Nlet villains all over the world know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our power that will...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...save the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're safe now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kizaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take Straw boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inazuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better stop, Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's finish this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you go any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New Kama Kempo: 44 - Aesthetic Technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laser Surgery Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My nails have melted!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emporio Ivankov of the Revolutionaries army!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You use strange techniques as they say!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New Kama Kempo: 44 - Aesthetic Technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fat Suctioning Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no time to play with you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I burned my lips, my lips, my lips...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or not! Because of \Nmy over-applied make-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Ivan-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them get away! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this too one-sided? \NWe already know who won...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defeat them decisively!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever let them even \Nthink about challenging us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll let them know...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...The power of justice that we own!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy them!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akainu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei! Hand Dragon's son over to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have an advantage once we \Nget to the sea! I can outrun him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! It's frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aokiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you've got nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It went right through Jimbei  \Nand got to Ace's brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't let him hurt anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my way, Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-kun, I'm sorry! I couldn't save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! You have to worry \Nabout yourself right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed a little because you were in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it hit his heart, it \Nwould've been easier for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so, Jimbei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna keep protecting \Nhim with a hole in his chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna die soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei, if I don't escape death...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry but could you \Nlook after my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not helping him because \Nhe is your brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a high regard for Luffy-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already made up my mind to save \Nhis life even if it means death!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let him die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I die,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let Luffy-kun die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:16:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sables!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody, catch them and \Nput them on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta protect the one you wanna protect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them have their way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that I got carried away, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.78,0:17:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end of Captain Buggy's legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your support all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not coming down...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He helped Straw Hat and Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy, you made us \Nbelieve that you were gonna run
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you helped your fellow escapee \NStraw Hat when it counted!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're beautiful and shimmering!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're being weird again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei and Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What made you guys fly in the \Nsky with blood all over you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, why is it so hot here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Magma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, red-nosed man! You helped us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going \Non and I'm not helping you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:19:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I allowed Luffy-kun to be injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He needs to be treated immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'm the one who needs help, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could we get him treated here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you call me "red-nosed man"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They keep getting in my way \Nwhen I'm about to get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rose Rondo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fools, one and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.77,0:19:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna die to save that Straw Hat brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've all seen his limitless tenacity \Nand power with our own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who Ace wanted \Nto save and Pops approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we're bound to bring \Nhim into the new era!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you all were better \Nthan that! Not that it matters!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Whitebeard Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akainu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The degree to which you see him as a \Nrisk - that makes you wanna kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The degree to which we have \Nhigh expectations of him -
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that makes us wanna protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the same, don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys got me involved again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Jimbei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that you're unconscious! \NWhere should I go now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.55,0:20:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether he lives or dies, \Nit's as if he's in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can make him suffer \Nas we please while he lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:21:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't resolve this \Nthrough dialogue anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sengoku vs. Blackbeard over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's Akainu vs. the commanders over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.76,0:21:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fighting hasn't stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy! Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all, fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.03,0:21:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break... Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, we reached the \Npoint where it's not frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.76,0:22:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.59,0:22:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?! The ship came out of water!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.42,0:22:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a submarine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that another enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose ship is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put Straw Hat-ya on my ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.28,0:22:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Straw Hat-ya"? That's really \Na strange way to call somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.13,0:22:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you, brat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.50,0:22:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat-ya will become \Nmy enemy at some stage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.88,0:22:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but a desirable relationship \Nis still a relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.00,0:23:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in letting him die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:06.36,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE HEART PIRATES--CAPTAIN TRAFALGAR LAW
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.27,0:23:04.61,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna help him get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.61,0:23:06.36,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take care of him for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.36,0:23:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.32,0:23:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.44,0:23:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy's relentless pursuit continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the meaningless battle rages on endlessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.59,0:23:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one young man stands lost \Nin grief on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sadness gives birth to \Na great power called courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.25,0:23:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,setting the very world in motion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Desperate Scream! Courageous \NMoments that Will Change the Future"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
